rows.label: qst200901_msg003
rows.name: If we don't hurry, it will be sold out!

rows.label: qst200901_msg004
rows.name:
What are you in such a
hurry to purchase, Kasane?

rows.label: qst200901_msg005
rows.name:
Bread! Bread! The Lucky
Sachiveria Bread!

rows.label: qst200901_msg015
rows.name:
I heard it's sold at the Tuuli
Bakery beneath the windmill.

rows.label: qst200901_msg007
rows.name:
It's bread made with
Sachiveria dough, which
is said to bring good luck.

rows.label: qst200901_msg008
rows.name:
I just heard about it from
the innkeeper's wife...

rows.label: qst200901_msg010
rows.name:
There's a rumor that eating the bread
brings happiness not just to the person
who eats it, but to those around them too!

rows.label: qst200901_msg013
rows.name:
It's an incredibly popular item,
so if you don't go early in the
morning, it'll be sold out!

rows.label: qst200901_msg014
rows.name:
Come on, come on! Let's hurry to
Tuuli Bakery before it's sold out!
